<bibRefCitation author="Nakamura" box="[395,595,1201,1225]" pageId="2" pageNumber="22" refString="Nakamura, M. (2004) A morphological and phylogenetic study on the pupae of Geometridae (Insecta: Lepidoptera) from Japan. Tinea, 18 (Suppl. 1), 1 - 227." type="journal article" year="2004">
